{"tid":461163,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"曾經好朋友變成陌生人好可惜（2）","createTime":"2017-11-07T10:19:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T15:51:00.000Z","uid":156308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"63a38837089f2a7194e688df5a6b5a661cbf37f3","tid":461163,"uid":156308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T10:19:47.000Z","msg":"上次送左首最佳損友比大家<br />\n一路打都覺得好唔開心 有絕望既感覺<br />\n出post發現原來好多人都有相似既經歷同感受 <br />\n<br />\n話說我訂左張道歉卡 <br />\n本黎諗住月尾寄比佢（月尾岩岩好嬲左我半年）<br />\n同埋諗住搵佢搵到佢肯原諒我為止<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/07/175250_0514c9806b6abe74fbbf7f349661327c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F175250_0514c9806b6abe74fbbf7f349661327c.jpg&h=00903599&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/07/175320_61211b6d525d99f1c1cb5f3d3873ee31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F175320_61211b6d525d99f1c1cb5f3d3873ee31.jpg&h=108b2641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但呢刻我突然心血來潮 決定唔寄唔再搵佢<br />\n放棄呢個朋友 <br />\n<br />\n諗起過去真係好美好 同佢做朋友好舒服同好開心<br />\n我一直好信任佢  信任既程度好比家人<br />\n而且我係一個好重視時間觀念既人，但無論佢放我幾多次飛機到最後我都一定原諒佢！（如果係其他朋友我唔會）<br />\n<br />\n識左咁耐 經歷過咁多事 <br />\n到最後連原因都唔肯講<br />\n一啲先兆都無就咁放棄左佢本黎話好重視既朋友&mdash;\u0000&mdash;\u0000\u0000我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n為左唔再日日為呢件事煩惱<br />\n我決定唔再執著落去<br />\n或者放棄 都係另一種解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家同我一樣 可以繼續向前行<br />\n唔好再停留係過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd57699ee41504a632870aaf861ca748b9890a64","tid":461163,"uid":203701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:51:00.000Z","msg":"..."}]}